    "transits.mercury.silverLiningTitle": "The Silver Lining",
    "transits.mercury.silverLining1": "While Mercury Retrograde is often viewed with apprehension, it offers valuable opportunities for growth and reflection. This is an excellent time to revisit old projects, reconnect with people from your past, and tie up loose ends.",
    "transits.mercury.silverLining2": "The retrograde period encourages us to slow down, review our communication patterns, and make necessary adjustments. Many people find that relationships improve after clearing up old misunderstandings during this time.",
    "transits.mercury.silverLining3": "Remember, Mercury Retrograde happens three to four times a year, and humanity has thrived through countless retrograde periods. With awareness and preparation, you can navigate this time successfully and even use it to your advantage.",
